<i>noun</i>: 허방 [허방], 탄광 [탄ː광], 심연 [시ː면], 수렁 [수렁], 땅굴 [땅꿀], 구멍 [구멍], 구렁텅이 [구렁텅이], 갱도 [갱도], 갱 [갱] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>허방 [허방]</dt><br>
<dd>pit; hollow; hole</dd><br>
<dd>땅바닥이 움푹 패어 빠지기 쉬운 구덩이.</dd><br>
<dd>A hollow, sunken hole in the ground, easy to fall into.</dd><br>
<dt>탄광 [탄ː광]</dt><br>
<dd>coal mine; pit</dd><br>
<dd>석탄을 캐내는 광산.</dd><br>
<dd>A mine where coal is dug up.</dd><br>
<dt>심연 [시ː면]</dt><br>
<dd>1. deep pond</dd><br>
<dd>깊은 연못.</dd><br>
<dd>A deep pond.</dd><br>
<dd>2. abyss; pit</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 매우 어렵고 절망적이어서 빠져나오기 힘든 상황이나 감정.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) A very difficult and desperate situation or emotion that one finds hard to escape.</dd><br>
<dd>3. abyss; depth</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 뛰어넘거나 극복하기 어려운 깊은 간격.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) A profound distance between two things or persons that one cannot jump over or overcome.</dd><br>
<dt>수렁 [수렁]</dt><br>
<dd>1. pit; mire</dd><br>
<dd>흙과 물이 뒤섞여 질퍽거리는 깊은 웅덩이.</dd><br>
<dd>A deep hole that is muddy due to a mixture of soil and water.</dd><br>
<dd>2. pit; mire</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 빠져나오기 힘든 안 좋은 상황.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) A bad situation difficult to get out.</dd><br>
<dt>땅굴 [땅꿀]</dt><br>
<dd>1. tunnel</dd><br>
<dd>땅속으로 뚫린 굴.</dd><br>
<dd>A path or road dug underground.</dd><br>
<dd>2. pit; hollow; burrow</dd><br>
<dd>땅을 깊고 길게 파서 굴과 같이 만든 큰 구덩이.</dd><br>
<dd>A long, deep hole made like a tunnel by digging in the ground.</dd><br>
<dt>구멍 [구멍]</dt><br>
<dd>1. hole; pit</dd><br>
<dd>뚫어지거나 파낸 자리.</dd><br>
<dd>An area sunken by drilling or digging.</dd><br>
<dd>2. way out; loophole</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 어려운 상황에서 벗어나는 길.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) A way to escape a difficult situation.</dd><br>
<dd>3. loophole; weakness</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 허점이나 약점.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) A loophole or weak point.</dd><br>
<dt>구렁텅이 [구렁텅이]</dt><br>
<dd>1. pit</dd><br>
<dd>몹시 험하고 깊게 움푹 파인 땅.</dd><br>
<dd>A deep hole hollowed extremely roughly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. abyss</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 벗어나기 아주 어려운 상태.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) a situation which is difficult to get out of.</dd><br>
<dt>갱도 [갱도]</dt><br>
<dd>gallery; pit; shaft</dd><br>
<dd>갱 안에서 광석을 나르거나 사람이 드나들도록 만들어 놓은 길.</dd><br>
<dd>A path in a pit to transport mined minerals and for people to come and go.</dd><br>
<dt>갱 [갱]</dt><br>
<dd>pit</dd><br>
<dd>광물을 파기 위해 땅속으로 파 들어간 굴.</dd><br>
<dd>A hole in the ground dug to mine minerals.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>